name: Split Personality Sunset
description:
Title: Split Personality Sunset
Location: Salem, Oregon
Year Taken: 2019
About this photo: I was waiting for my clients to do a family portrait session at Salem Riverfront Park. It had recently rained in the area, in between rain showers in fact. We had a moment where the weather was just right for exploring the park for finding photographic gems. This was just a puddle with a reflection that I really liked. What I did in post production made it really fun. I brought an orange hue to the sky and kept a nice blue in the puddle, making a split personality sunset that adds extra character to this fun piece of colorful artwork.
